Looking for an affordable portable monitor that works with just about anything? The MSI PRO MP165 E6 is a budget-friendly 15.6” portable display designed for handheld gaming PCs, mini PCs, laptops, and even smartphones. In this video, we test the MP165 E6 with handhelds, Windows mini PCs, and more to see if it’s the best budget portable monitor for gaming, productivity, and travel.
Whether you’re gaming on the go, extending your laptop screen, or hooking it up to a mini PC, the MSI PRO MP165 E6 offers a lightweight and versatile solution. Let’s find out if it’s worth picking up!
